        "tree_id": "70ca5990d27dacd8c8fd1728891dbccbabacfc04",
        "message": "chore(deps): bump openai 4.78 -> 6.38 (@mch/editorial-pilot)\n\nopenai SDK v4 -> v6 covers two majors:\n- v5: migrated from node-fetch to built-in fetch (transparent for our\n  usage; we never set a custom httpAgent or relied on node-fetch types)\n- v6: ResponseFunctionToolCallOutputItem.output and ResponseCustomToolCallOutput.output\n  shapes changed (only relevant for the Responses API tool-calling\n  surface; we exclusively use chat.completions which is unaffected)\n\nOur editorial-pilot client uses:\n- new OpenAI({ apiKey, timeout, maxRetries }) -> stable since v4\n- client.chat.completions.create(...) -> stable since v4\n- response.choices[0].message.content, response.usage.{prompt,completion}_tokens\n  -> stable since v4\n\nVerification: typecheck + lint + test:unit + build all green (18/18\ntasks). No code changes required.\n\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>",
        "timestamp": "2026-05-22T08:33:54Z",
